Class I2B2Factory

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.i2b2.api.I2B2Factory

  • public class I2B2Factory
extends java.lang.Object
    The i2b2 Factory provides a connection to an i2b2 instance. It manages all the projects and individual cell connections.

    Jeremy R. Easton-Marks
